<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Membership Reminder</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: left;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <p>Dear {{firstName}},</p>
    <p>This is a reminder for your upcoming payment for the Fitness+ {{membershipType}} membership. Your due date is {{dueDate}}.</p>
    {{#if isFirstMonth}}
        <p>Your first payment includes the annual membership fee of ${{totalAmount}} and the first month's add-on services fee of ${{monthlyAmount}}.</p>
    {{else}}
        <p>Your monthly add-on services fee is ${{monthlyAmount}}.</p>
    {{/if}}
    <p>Please visit the following link to view your invoice: <a href="{{invoiceLink}}">{{invoiceLink}}</a></p>
    <p>Thank you,</p>
    <p>Fitness+ Team</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
